er/Notation.html#Top.top\">⊤</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log_top","kind":"theorem","line":53,"name":"ENNReal.log_top","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.lean#L53-L53"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log_one\"><span class=\"name\">ENNReal</span>.<span class=\"name\">log_one</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log\">log</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log_one","kind":"theorem","line":52,"name":"ENNReal.log_one","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.lean#L52-L52"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log_zero\"><span class=\"name\">ENNReal</span>.<span class=\"name\">log_zero</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log\">log</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Notation.html#Bot.bot\">⊥</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log_zero","kind":"theorem","line":51,"name":"ENNReal.log_zero","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.lean#L51-L51"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">noncomputable def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log\"><span class=\"name\">ENNReal</span>.<span class=\"name\">log</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/ENNReal/Basic.html#ENNReal\">ENNReal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/EReal/Basic.html#EReal\">EReal</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The logarithm function defined on the extended nonnegative reals `ℝ≥0∞`\nto the extended reals `EReal`. Coincides with the usual logarithm function\nand with `Real.log` on positive reals, and takes values `log 0 = ⊥` and `log ⊤ = ⊤`.\nConventions about multiplication in `ℝ≥0∞` and addition in `EReal` make the identity\n`log (x * y) = log x + log y` unconditional. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.html#ENNReal.log","kind":"def","line":41,"name":"ENNReal.log","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/ENNRealLog.lean#L41-L49"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.Pow.NNReal","Mathlib.Data.EReal.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.Log.ENNRealLog"}